=== CANONICALIZATION REDIRECTS (301 PERMANENT) ===

Ensures all traffic uses HTTPS and the non-www domain, consolidating SEO authority.

1. Force HTTPS (HTTP to HTTPS)

https://www.google.com/search?q=http://spotongifts.co.za/* https://www.google.com/search?q=https://spotongifts.co.za/:splat  301
https://www.google.com/search?q=http://www.spotongifts.co.za/* https://www.google.com/search?q=https://spotongifts.co.za/:splat  301

2. Force Non-WWW (WWW to Non-WWW)

https://www.google.com/search?q=https://www.spotongifts.co.za/* https://www.google.com/search?q=https://spotongifts.co.za/:splat  301

3. Clean up the index file (e.g., /index.html should be the root /)

/index.html / 301